Example (required name and age object):
```json
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "name": {"type": "string"},
    "age": {"type": "integer"}
  },
  "required": ["name", "age"]
}
```

**Note**: This field must not be specified when the `type` is set to `"text"`.
